#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:183
msgid "When we ask you for personal data"
msgstr "Tra gofynnwn ni am wybodaeth bersonol"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:185
msgid "We promise to inform you why we need your personal data and ask only for the personal data we need and not collect information that is irrelevant or excessive."
msgstr "Rydyn ni’n addo i roi gwybod i chi pam mae angen eich data personol chi, dim ond i ofyn am y data personol rydyn ni ei angen, ac i beidio casglu gwybodaeth sy’n amherthnasol neu’n ormodol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:189
msgid "When we collect your personal data, we have responsibilities, and you have rights. These include:"
msgstr "Pan yr ydyn ni’n casglu eich data personol, mae gennym ni gyfrifoldebau, a mae gennych chi hawliau, gan gynnwys:"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:194
msgid "That you can withdraw consent at any time, where relevant;"
